  m_text: "Terese,\r\nThings haven\u2019t been easy between us lately. But now is
    not the time for grudges you need to focus on staying safe. Listen to me.\r\nThe
    checkpoint has gotten stricter, long inspections, trap questions, sometimes people
    get turned away without explanation."
